data.description: Welcome to this beautiful, charming cape situated on a level corner lot! This house has delightful curb appeal to go along its level long driveway. Inside, you are immediately greeted with a beautiful marble foyer that leads to a spacious living room adjacent to a formal dining area. Located across the way, you will find an beautiful kitchen with center island (and seating for two) that ends at a breakfast nook large enough to fit another dining table. An updated powder room and private laundry room with access to an attached 2 car garage completes the main level. Upstairs you will find three bedrooms with a large full bath and two walk in closets. Love the outdoors? Access to the large level yard is available via the sliding glass doors from the kitchen or formal dining room. Plenty of parking with a spacious driveway leading to the attached 2 car garage.
